{
  "info": {
    "name": "Nexus Platform API",
    "description": "Complete API collection for Nexus Investor-Entrepreneur Collaboration Platform\n\n## Features\n- JWT Authentication with 2FA/OTP\n- Real-time Chat & Video Calling\n- Meeting Scheduling with Conflict Detection\n- Document Management with E-Signature\n- Mock Payment System\n\n## Setup Instructions\n1. Import this collection into Postman\n2. Set the `base_url` variable to your server URL (default: http://localhost:5000)\n3. Register a new user or login\n4. The JWT token will be automatically set in the `token` variable\n5. All authenticated requests will use this token automatically\n\n## Variables\n- `base_url`: API base URL (http://localhost:5000)\n- `token`: JWT token (auto-set after login)\n- `user_id`: Current user ID (auto-set after login)\n- `other_user_id`: Another user's ID for testing\n- `meeting_id`: Meeting ID for testing\n- `document_id`: Document ID for testing",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_exporter_id": "nexus-platform"
  },
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [
      {
        "key": "token",
        "value": "{{token}}",
        "type": "string"
      }
    ]
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "base_url",
      "value": "http://localhost:5000",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "token",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "user_id",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "other_user_id",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "meeting_id",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "document_id",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Authentication",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Register User",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
                  "    const response = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.environment.set('token', response.token);",
                  "    pm.environment.set('user_id', response._id);",
                  "    pm.test('Registration successful', () => {",
                  "        pm.expect(response).to.have.property('token');",
                  "    });",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": {
              "type": "noauth"
            },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"John Entrepreneur\",\n  \"email\": \"john@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\",\n  \"role\": \"entrepreneur\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/register",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "register"]
            },
            "description": "Register a new user account. Role can be 'entrepreneur' or 'investor'."
          },
          "response": []
        },
